
Repository licensing summary
----------------------------

This repository uses multiple licenses for different parts of the tree.
Full license references and canonical texts are provided in the
`LICENCES/` directory.

Per-directory license mapping (SPDX identifiers):

- `kernel/` : GNU General Public License v3.0 only
	- SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-only
	- See: LICENCES/GPL-3.0.txt

- `usr/` : BSD 3-Clause "New" or "Revised" License
	- SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause
	- See: LICENCES/BSD-3-Clause.txt

- `docs/` : Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
	- SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-SA-4.0
	- See: LICENCES/CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt

- build system and related top-level build scripts (e.g. `scripts/`,
  SCons helpers):
	- SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause
	- See: LICENCES/BSD-3-Clause.txt

Notes:
- Files not mentioned above are covered by the SPDX identifiers at the
  top of the file.
- SPDX identifiers above are authoritative short identifiers for the
  stated licenses. The full texts (or links to canonical texts) are
  included in the `LICENCES/` directory.

